AddressInfo.Title: Spurn Point
AddressInfo.AccessComments: 2x 7kw Type 2. Important: Ask in cafe for RFID card, DO NOT connect cable to either end until card tapped on reader! Return card to cafe and repeat process to disconnect. Cost 25p/kWh, note kWh used from unit and pay in cafe when finished. Bit of a faff. Good cake though.

GeneralComments: Car park open dawn until dusk. The Spurn Discovery Centre is open 09:00 - 17:00 (16:00 in winter), with the cafe open 10:00 - 16:00 (15:00 in winter).
